Interface Stack<E>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    LinkedStack

    public interface Stack<E>
    Stack Abstract Data Type. A Stack is a linear data structure following last-in-first-out protocol, i.e. the last element that has been added onto the Stack, is the first one to be removed.

    • Method Summary
